<h2>Complete work item information</h2>

<p>To ensure your work item has all required information, use the <strong>Tasks</strong> page from the left sidebar menu. This page shows all incomplete information for work items where you are the owner, SRO, or service owner.</p>

<h3>Required information</h3>
<p>The following information must be completed for each work item:</p>

<ul>
    <li><strong>At least 1 team member</strong> - Add team members via the Team tab</li>
    <li><strong>SRO (Senior Responsible Officer)</strong> - Add via the Overview tab</li>
    <li><strong>At least 1 directorate</strong> - Add via the Overview tab</li>
    <li><strong>Activity type</strong> - Set via the Overview tab</li>
    <li><strong>RAG status</strong> - Set via the RAG tracking tab</li>
    <li><strong>Business area</strong> - Set via the Overview tab</li>
    <li><strong>Aim</strong> - Enter via the Overview tab</li>
    <li><strong>At least 1 primary contact</strong> - Set via the Overview tab</li>
    <li><strong>Budget owner</strong> - Set via the Overview tab</li>
</ul>

<h3>How to complete information</h3>
<ol>
    <li>Go to the <strong>Tasks</strong> page from the left sidebar</li>
    <li>Review the list of incomplete tasks for your work items</li>
    <li>Click <strong>Complete</strong> next to each task to go directly to the relevant section</li>
    <li>Fill in the required information and save</li>
    <li>Return to the Tasks page to verify the task has been removed</li>
</ol>

<p>Completing all work item information helps ensure accurate reporting and better visibility of your work item's status.</p>

